[embed]https://youtu.be/VbLtq2NLrpc[/embed] This semi-automatic eyelet machine takes all of the hard work out of setting eyelets/grommets, Compatible with 8mm, self-punching eyelets (available separately). In one action, the machine will punch a hole and affix 6mm eyelets to your chosen fabric. With minimal effort, up to 1800 eyelets can be set per hour Hopper holds up to 500 eyelets at any time, Extra-deep throat depth of 165mm, Powder-coated iron construction. It’s an incredibly time-efficient machine that puts an end to having to set a grommet on a die before every use. Simply pour the eyelets into the hopper and they will automatically feed down the channel. When you pull down on the lever, the die ‘picks up’ an eyelet before fixing to the fabric. Once finished, the next eyelet will slide into place Easy to use thanks to its extra-long handle and soft-touch grip, Set on rollers, it can easily be moved along the length of whatever you’re fixing grommets The perfect machine for your corsets, DIY projects, leathercraft, handbag, clothing, scrapbooking, documents and much more, Ideal for home or professional use.
